\c 4
\s Ukulingwa kukaJesu
\p
\v 1 Kwathi uJesu egcwele uMoya oNgcwele\x + Mat. 4.1-11. Mark. 1.12,13.\x* wabuya evela eJordani\x + 3.3,21.\x*, wakhokhelelwa nguMoya enkangala\x + 2.27. 4.14.\x*,
\v 2 walingwa ngudiyabhola insuku ezingamatshumi amane\x + Mark. 1.13.\x*. Njalo kadlanga lutho ngalezonsuku; kwathi seziphelile, ekucineni walamba.
\v 3 Udiyabhola wasesithi kuye: Uba uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu, tshono kulelilitshe ukuthi libe yisinkwa.
\v 4 UJesu wasemphendula, wathi: Kulotshiwe, ukuthi umuntu kayikuphila ngesinkwa sodwa, kodwa ngalo lonke ilizwi likaNkulunkulu\x + Dute. 8.3.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Udiyabhola wasemkhokhelela entabeni ende\x + Mat. 4.8-10.\x* wamtshengisa yonke imibuso yomhlaba ngesikhatshana\x + Mat. 24.14.\x*.
\v 6 Udiyabhola wasesithi kuye: Amandla wonke la lobukhosi bayo ngizakunika\x + Joha. 12.31. Isam. 13.2.\x*; ngoba anikwe mina, njalo ngiwanika loba ngubani engithandayo\x + Joha. 12.31. Isam. 13.2.\x*.
\v 7 Ngakho wena uba ukhonza phambi kwami, konke kuzakuba ngokwakho.
\v 8 UJesu wasemphendula wathi: Suka ngemva kwami, Sathane; ngoba kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Uzakhothamela eNkosini uNkulunkulu wakho, njalo umkhonze yena yedwa\x + Dute. 6.13.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Wasemkhokhelela eJerusalema, wammisa engqongeni yethempeli\x + Mat. 4.5-7.\x*, wasesithi kuye: Uba uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu, ziwisele phansi usuka lapha;
\v 10 ngoba kulotshiwe ukuthi: Uzalaya ingilosi zakhe ngawe, ukukulondoloza;
\v 11 lokuthi: Zizakuphatha ngezandla, hlezi loba nini ukhube unyawo lwakho elitsheni\x + Hlab. 91.11,12.\x*.
\v 12 UJesu wasephendula wathi kuye: Kuthiwa: Ungayilingi iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho\x + Dute. 6.16.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Udiyabhola eseqedile ukulinga konke, wasuka kuye kwaze kwaba \add ngesinye\add* isikhathi\x + Seb. 13.11. Luka 22.28. Joha. 14.30. Heb. 2.18; 4.15.\x*.
\s UJesu uqala ukutshumayela
\p
\v 14 UJesu wasebuyela\x + Mat. 4.12.\x* eGalili\x + Seb. 10.37.\x* ngamandla kaMoya\x + 4.1.\x*; lendumela yakhe yaphuma kuso sonke isigaba esizingelezeleyo\x + Mat. 4.24.\x*.
\v 15 Yena wasefundisa emasinagogeni abo\x + 4.44. Mat. 4.23.\x*, edunyiswa yibo bonke\x + Mat. 15.31.\x*.
\s UJesu udelelwa ngabeNazaretha
\p
\v 16 Wasefika\x + Mat. 13.54-58. Mark. 6.1-6.\x* eNazaretha\x + Mat. 2.23. Luka 4.23.\x*, lapho ayondliwe khona\x + 2.39,51.\x*; njengokwejwayela kwakhe wasengena esinagogeni ngosuku lwesabatha\x + 4.44. Mat. 4.23.\x*, wasukuma ukuze afunde\x + Seb. 13.14,15; 17.2.\x*.
\v 17 Wasenikwa ugwalo lomprofethi uIsaya\x + Seb. 13.27; 15.21. Neh. 8.5-8.\x*. Waseluvula ugwalo\x + 4.20.\x*, wayithola indawo okubhalwe kuyo \add ukuthi\add*:
\v 18 UMoya weNkosi uphezu kwami, ngakho ingigcobile ukuthi ngitshumayele ivangeli kubayanga; ingithumile ukusilisa abadabukileyo enhliziyweni; ukumemezela ukukhululwa kwabathunjiweyo\x + Isa. 61.1,2.\x*, lokubona kwabayiziphofu\x + Isa. 61.1.\x*, ukukhulula ababandezelweyo\x + Isa. 58.6.\x*,
\v 19 ukumemezela\x + Isa. 61.1,2.\x* umnyaka womusa weNkosi\x + 4.24. 2 Kor. 6.2. Levi 25.8-17.\x*.
\v 20 Waselugoqa ugwalo\x + 4.20.\x*, wa\add lu\add*buyisela encekwini\x + Mat. 26.58.\x*, wahlala phansi; lamehlo abo bonke ababesesinagogeni amjolozela\x + 22.56. Seb. 1.10; 3.4,12; 6.15; 7.55; 10.4; 11.6; 13.9; 14.9; 23.1. 2 Kor. 3.7,13.\x*.
\v 21 Waseqala ukuthi kubo: Lamuhla lumbhalo ugcwalisekile endlebeni zenu.
\p
\v 22 Labo bonke bafakaza ngaye, bamangala ngamazwi omusa aphuma emlonyeni wakhe\x + Hlab. 45.2.\x*, basebesithi: Lo kayisiyo indodana kaJosefa yini\x + 3.23.\x*?
\v 23 Wasesithi kubo: Isibili lizakutsho kimi lesisaga: Melaphi, zelaphe wena\x + Mat. 27.40.\x*; konke lokho esikuzwileyo okwenzeke eKapenawume\x + Mat. 4.13,23,24; 11.23. Joha. 4.46-54.\x*, kwenze lalapha emzini wakini\x + Mat. 13.54,57. Mark. 6.1,4. Joha. 4.44. Luka 4.16. 2.39.\x*.
\v 24 Wathi-ke: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Kakho umprofethi\x + Mat. 13.57.\x* owemukelekayo\x + 4.24. 2 Kor. 6.2. Levi 25.8-17.\x* elizweni lakibo\x + Mat. 13.54,57. Mark. 6.1,4. Joha. 4.44. Luka 4.16. 2.39.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa ngeqiniso ngithi kini: Abafelokazi abanengi\x + 1 Kho. 17.9.\x* babekhona koIsrayeli ensukwini zikaElija\x + 4.23,24.\x*, lapho izulu lalivalekile iminyaka emithathu lenyanga eziyisithupha, kwaze kwaba khona indlala enkulu emhlabeni wonke\x + Jak. 5.17. 1 Kho. 17.1; 18.1.\x*;
\v 26 kodwa uElija kathunyelwanga lakomunye wabo, ngaphandle kweSarepita\x + 1 Kho. 17.9.\x* yeSidoni kowesifazana \add ong\add*umfelokazi\x + Seb. 27.3. Mat. 15.21.\x*.
\v 27 Futhi amalephero amanengi\x + 2 Kho. 5.1,14.\x* ayekhona koIsrayeli ngesikhathi sikaElisha umprofethi; kodwa kakuhlanjululwanga lamunye wawo, ngaphandle kukaNamani umSiriya\x + 4.23,24.\x*.
\v 28 Kwathi bonke ababesesinagogeni bagcwala ulaka, bezizwa lezizinto,
\v 29 basebesukuma, bamkhuphela ngaphandle komuzi\x + Seb. 7.58. Nani 15.35.\x*, bamqhubela eliweni lentaba umuzi wabo owawakhiwe phezu kwayo, ukuze bamphosele phansi eliweni.
\v 30 Kodwa yena edabula phakathi kwabo wahamba\x + Joha. 8.59. Joha. 10.39. Luka 24.31.\x*.
\s Ukusiliswa kwezigulane eKapenawume
\p
\v 31 Wasesehlela eKapenawume umuzi weGalili; njalo wayebafundisa ngamasabatha\x + Mat. 4.13. Mark. 1.21-28.\x*.
\v 32 Basebebabaza ngemfundiso yakhe\x + Mat. 7.28,29.\x*, ngoba ilizwi lakhe lalilamandla\x + 4.36. 1 Kor. 2.4.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Futhi kwakukhona esinagogeni umuntu owayelomoya wedimoni ongcolileyo, wasememeza ngelizwi elikhulu,
\v 34 wathi: Yekela! Silani lawe, Jesu mNazaretha? Uze ukusibhubhisa yini? Ngiyakwazi wena ukuthi ungubani: ONgcwele kaNkulunkulu\x + 4.41. Mat. 25.24.\x*.
\v 35 UJesu wasemkhuza, esithi: Thula, uphume kuye\x + 4.41. Mat. 25.24.\x*! Ledimoni selimwisele phakathi laphuma kuye, lingamlimazanga.
\v 36 Kwasekubafikela bonke ukumangala, bakhulumisana, besithi: Yilizwi bani leli, ukuthi ngegunya langamandla uyalaya omoya abangcolileyo, baphume\x + 4.33.\x*?
\v 37 Yasiphuma indumela yakhe kuyo yonke indawo yesigaba esizingelezeleyo.
\s Uninazala kaPetro labanye abagulayo bayasiliswa
\p
\v 38 Wasesukuma\x + Mat. 8.14-16. Mark. 1.29-34.\x* waphuma esinagogeni, wayangena endlini kaSimoni\x + 4.33.\x*; njalo uninazala kaSimoni wayebanjwe luqhuqho olukhulu; basebemcelela kuye.
\v 39 Wasemengama, wakhuza uqhuqho, khona lwamyekela; njalo wahle wasukuma wabasebenzela\x + Mat. 8.26. Mark. 4.39. Luka 8.24. 4.41.\x*.
\p
\v 40 Kwathi ekutshoneni kwelanga, bonke ababelababegula izifo ezitshiyeneyo babaletha kuye\x + Mark. 1.32.\x*; wasebeka izandla kulowo lalowo wabo wabasilisa\x + 13.13.\x*.
\v 41 Kwasekuphuma lamadimoni kwabanengi\x + Mark. 3.11,12.\x*, ememeza esithi: Wena unguKristu\x + Seb. 8.7.\x* iNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 14.33.\x*. Wase\add wa\add*khuza\x + Mark. 1.25. Luka 4.34,35. Mat. 12.16.\x* engawavumeli\x + Mark. 3.11,12.\x* ukuthi akhulume, ngoba ayemazi ukuthi unguKristu.
\s UJesu usuka eKapenawume
\p
\v 42 Kwathi sekusile, waphuma waya endaweni eyinkangala\x + Mark. 1.35-39.\x*, lamaxuku amdinga, eza kuye, amvimbela ukuthi angasuki kiwo\x + Mark. 1.36.\x*.
\v 43 Kodwa wathi kuwo: Ngimele ukutshumayela ivangeli lombuso kaNkulunkulu lakweminye imizi; ngoba ngithunyelwe lokho.
\v 44 Wayesetshumayela emasinagogeni eGalili\x + Mat. 4.23-25.\x*.